      Classes in org.optaplanner.core.api.score.buildin.hardsoftdouble that implement ScoreHolder 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  HardSoftDoubleScoreHolder
      Deprecated. 
      Double-based scores are deprecated as floating point numbers are not associative (A + B + C == C + B + A) and therefore they are not compatible with incremental score calculation. Use HardSoftBigDecimalScoreHolder or a scaled HardSoftLongScoreHolder instead.
